{
  "stem": "24397.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I could remember my mother feeling very upset-- and my father-- in listening to these speeches and not fully understanding what was being said but knowing that this was something bad for us.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, you know, and this happened on more than one occasions when our neighbors came in to listen.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I don't recall any discussion regarding the speeches, but they went on for hours and-- very heated type of speeches.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You may have heard them on some of these shows occasionally.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so I think this was the first indication that something bad is looming up there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The next thing I knew that some of my school pals were being enlisted into-- well, I think they were too young for the Hitler Youth.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was another thing called [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Deutsche Jugend, DJ.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the younger kids went into that, and so--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eight, nine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The same age as I was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so they would-- everybody was getting a uniform.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There was a spirit, to some degree.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You might say it was contagious, because, you know, everybody was busy being involved in things and bands being formed and people marching around.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was on the outside looking in, not-- in some ways perhaps, envious.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The not being part of all this new adventure.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And yet, at the same time, knowing that there was something unhealthy about it as far as I was concerned.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Although the kids at that time still used to come, and they used to show me what they got.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they had these little daggers, and we'd play with those things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then on another occasion-- militarism started becoming very evident.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
